{"title":"中国，期盼七月","authors":["赵玉亮"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":5,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，期盼七月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵玉亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的七月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一坛酿制了百年的老酒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正等待着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"启封"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一个多么漫长的过程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几代人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在焦灼的渴盼中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"容纳苦难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗刷耻辱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨砺斗志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"审度时机……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经一位老人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巧妙点化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熔炼得炉火纯青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戛然把这个日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圈定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拂去浮尘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滤掉酸辛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉淀成一种东方智慧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝聚成一种时代合力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升华成一种民族精神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海一样深邃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天一样透明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能抚摸伤痛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能启悟心智"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能激发豪情……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来，所有的同胞们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们期盼七月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高举起酒杯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从北向南"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"期盼着架起一道万里长虹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为告别沉重的昨天干杯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为欢呼辉煌的今天干杯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为创造美好的明天干杯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把七月的历史瞬间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一饮而尽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在世界的瞳仁里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊喜成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世纪末的美丽风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：总参工程兵某部）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}